{"title":"外国谚语","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":10,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"外国谚语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△知识蕴藏在谦虚的大海中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（朝鲜）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△知识使人谦虚，无知使人骄傲。 （英国）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△有志者自有千方百计，无志者只感千难万难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（印度尼西亚）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△土地需要辛勤耕耘，知识需要不断探索。（尼泊尔）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"△不学习的人象不长谷物的荒地。（印度）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}